{"tid":2083233,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"從來抗爭唔係包贏","createTime":"2020-06-28T15:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:40:33.000Z","uid":283700,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03b6b6ca083df65b9c05a4074f47cbd31cd016ab","tid":2083233,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"抗爭有贏有輸。 即使輸我地要敵方付出代價就得，之鋒走啦 咪傻鳩係香港。<br />\n<br />\n我地現在最需要既係建立一套抗爭手段，外判抗爭係最岩香港人既方法，一個號稱國際城市，拒絕人入境係幾難既事，外判比東南亞 中東 南北非吧<br />\n<br />\n其次，係教育上要一代傳一代<br />\n<br />\n最後，繼續排警畜。要佢地今生今世都圍爐取暖。  盡量要做到旅行都要佢地去唔成，去咩國家都當佢地係極危險人物就得。"},{"pid":"dd95101e5f591ccb9c64cb6eb2fa2d2dc03f6066","tid":2083233,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"c4f4142c404b8418a61afd5415678a1f05030835","tid":2083233,"uid":2746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pBnePd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pBnePd.gif&h=d1d0a7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHXBjiU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHXBjiU.gif&h=cbd0bceb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2419055b6f13d3640e1ddcbbda64a85f78575a","tid":2083233,"uid":2746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pBnePd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pBnePd.gif&h=d1d0a7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHXBjiU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHXBjiU.gif&h=cbd0bceb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aef511075e63e2f1c318392968244210af33e3d","tid":2083233,"uid":279963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"同埋我想講嘅係，抗爭輸左唔代表以後都輸晒。<br />\n成日講運動已完係冇意義。静左亦唔等於係&quot;對唔住手足&quot;, 真正嘅輸，係當我地完全放棄，唔再反抗，唔再關心。<br />\n<br />\n只要我地仲有反抗